gobblin.metrics.event

Class TimingEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.metrics.event.TimingEvent

  • public class TimingEvent
extends Object
    Event to time actions in the program. Automatically reports start time, end time, and duration from the time the TimingEvent was created to the time stop() is called.

        public void stop()

        public void stop(Map<String,String> additionalMetadata)
        Stop the timer and submit the event, along with the additional metadata specified. If the timer was already stopped before, this is a no-op.
        Parameters:
        additionalMetadata - a Map of additional metadata that should be submitted along with this event
